sentence: Cheney, however, is facing a primary challenger, Harriet Hageman, who was endorsed by former President Donald Trump last September and who may have an easier time getting financial backing thanks to a rule change.
author: Rebecca Downs
title: Some Laughably Irrelevant Figures Are Trying to Insert Themselves into the Liz Cheney Censure Conversation
